英国奖2025年：萨布丽娜·卡彭特（Sabrina Carpenter）确认表演https://www.nme.com/news/music/music/brit-awards-2025-sabrina-carpenter-confenter-confirmed-to-perform-3836811?utm_source = rs = rss间表演Surej SinghTue, 11 Feb 2025 06:05:42 +0000 Music NewsNewsBRIT AwardsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3836811 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>她还将获得享有声望的全球成功奖</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-sabrina-carpenter-confirmed-to-perform-3836811">英国邮政2025年：萨布丽娜·卡彭特（Sabrina Carpenter）确认表演</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">萨布丽娜·卡彭特（Sabrina Carpenter）</a>已被确认将在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/brit-awards">2025年英国颁奖典礼</a>上演出 - 在下面了解更多信息。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-nominees-3831514">这是2025年英国奖的所有提名人</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.brits.co.uk/news/2025/sabrina-carpenter-to-perform-and-wins-global-success/#:~:text=wins%20Global%20Success-,Sabrina%20Carpenter%20to%20perform%20and%20wins%20Global%20Success,Sheeran%2C%20Adele%20and%20Sam%20Smith." target="_blank" rel="noopener">英国人宣布</a>，“浓缩咖啡”和“请请”杀手萨布丽娜·卡彭特（Sabrina Carpenter）将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/date-revealed-for-the-brit-awards-2025-3794739">在3月1日星期六在伦敦的O2举行的</a>仪式上，并专门在ITV1和ITVX上播出。</p><p>她不仅会在场，而且她会在舞台上表演，尽管有关她将要执行的内容的详细信息仍在包裹中。</p><p>此外，Carpenter将在今年的仪式上获得享有盛誉的全球成功奖。她将加入一个被授予独家奖项的行为精英名册 - 过去的获奖者仅限于<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/one-direction">一个方向</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ed-sheeran">埃德·希兰（Ed Sheeran）</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/adele">阿黛尔（Adele</a> ）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-smith">萨姆·史密斯（Sam Smith）</a> 。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DF57owDI_Se/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-gr